  <div class="container series-head">
    <h1>Before The Shop Numbers</h1>
    <p>The CFD began purchasing motorized apparatus in earnest in 1911. Many of these early vehicles didn't last long enough to receive a brass plaque with shop number in early 1923. Numbering on this page comes from the excellent Ken Little/John McNalis History of Chicago Firehouses (volumes I - IV).</p>
